title: DDResampled 2013 Full Versions Preview Mix
description:
A big update is in store for the DDResampled Full Versions collection. This mix is a sneak peek at what is to come. It exclusively features music not included in the previous Full Versions release and that will be included in the next release.

Technical details:

Single-file FLAC @ level 7(CUE sheet not included)
Length: 1:20:35 (Should be overburnable to most 80-minute CD-Rs)

A CUE sheet for this mix will be released along with the update's release.

A release date for the update has not been determined.

The use of the tracks in the compilation independently is not recommended as most tracks are intermixed in some way. One is shortened. All have been volume-leveled using Tootie's custom volume-leveling procedure.
